data.description: Exceptional investment in an ideal location! This newly renovated 3-unit property showcases extensive upgrades, including new electrical systems, flooring, paint, and lighting. Seize the opportunity to capitalize on this prime investment - live in one unit while renting out the other two, or maximize your returns by leasing all three units. Hard to find a 3 Unit at this price point, making this a unique and valuable find. Conveniently situated near major thoroughfares such as 131 and I96, as well as shopping destinations, this residence is strategically positioned within the coveted Leonard St. corridor. Do not let this opportunity pass by - schedule your showing now and secure your stake in this great property!
